                            <h4 style="font-weight: 400;font-size: 1.4rem;">VentureCrowd CEO Steve Maarbani spoke to Ticker INVEST about mortgage fund investing.
                            </h4>
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                            <p>
                                Watch the recording of the interview below.
                            </p>
                            <div class="fluid-video-wrapper">
                                <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/DQUPPnUEQrY" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"></iframe>
